<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧٢٠٨ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2956">أَبُو عَاصِمٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/7044">يَزِيدَ بْنِ أَبِي عُبَيْدٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2534">سَلَمَةَ </a>قَالَ:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٧٩⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span> <span class="c2">«بَايَعْنَا النَّبِيَّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> تَحْتَ الشَّجَرَةِ،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ لِي:</span> يَا سَلَمَةُ أَلَا تُبَايِعُ.<span class="c5"> قُلْتُ:</span> يَا رَسُولَ اللهِ، قَدْ بَايَعْتُ فِي الْأَوَّلِ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> وَفِي الثَّانِي.»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>